></td><td class=\"trend-up\"><strong>+19%</strong></td><td class=\"trend-up\"><strong>+27%</strong></td></tr>\n      <tr><td>软件许可证</td><td>116</td><td>183</td><td class=\"trend-down\">-37%</td><td class=\"trend-down\">-33%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>软件支持</td><td>2,469</td><td>2,761</td><td class=\"trend-down\">-11%</td><td class=\"trend-down\">-6%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td><strong>云+软件合计</strong></td><td><strong>8,548</strong></td><td><strong>7,938</strong></td><td class=\"trend-up\"><strong>+8%</strong></td><td class=\"trend-up\"><strong>+14%</strong></td></tr>\n      <tr><td>服务收入</td><td>1,007</td><td>1,075</td><td class=\"trend-down\">-6%</td><td>-1%</td></tr>\n      <tr style=\"background:#eef3fc\"><td><strong>总营收</strong></td><td><strong>9,555</strong></td><td><strong>9,013</strong></td><td class=\"trend-up\"><strong>+6%</strong></td><td class=\"trend-up\"><strong>+12%</strong></td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <div class=\"highlight-row\">\n    <div class=\"highlight-item\"><div class=\"hl-label\">云收入占比（总营收）</div><div class=\"hl-value\">62.4% <span class=\"trend-up\">↑ (2025同期55.4%)</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"highlight-item\"><div class=\"hl-label\">云毛利率 (IFRS)</div><div class=\"hl-value\">74.6% <span class=\"trend-up\">↑ +0.1pp</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"highlight-item\"><div class=\"hl-label\">云ERP Suite占SaaS/PaaS</div><div class=\"hl-value\">88.4% <span>核心引擎</span></div></div>\n    <div class=\"highlight-item\"><div class=\"hl-label\">软件支持收入降幅</div><div class=\"hl-value\">-11% <span class=\"trend-down\">↓ 客户加速迁云</span></div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <h4>🔍 收入结构洞察</h4>\n    <p>云ERP Suite增速(+30% cc)三倍于总营收增速，\"RISE with SAP\"全栈云迁移战略效果显著。软件支持收入加速下滑(-11%)是客户主动从传统维护向云订阅迁移的结果。IaaS收入+156%反映BTP和Business Data Cloud快速采纳。</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 3. 盈利能力 -->\n<div class=\"section\">\n  <div class=\"section-title\"><span class=\"icon\">📉</span> 三、盈利质量与利润率分析</div>\n  <table>\n    <thead><tr><th>指标 (€百万)</th><th>Q1 2026